  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Prospective study on the effect of partial wrist denervation (ie combined anterior and
      posterior interosseous neurectomy) on pain relief on functional outcome in patient with wrist
      osteoarthritis. The impact of psychological factors on postoperative outcome will be studied.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
